rsify with Bandcamp exclusives  \n\n**Success Metrics**  \n- YouTube 1K \u2192 10K subs in 6 months  \n- Stabilize Spotify listeners at 35K\u00b15% variance  \n- 75% reduced follower drop-off post-releases  \n\n---  \n*All materials current as of January 2025. Full analytics annex available upon request.*"
